==English==
===Noun===
'''impetigo''' (''plural'' '''impetigos''')

# {{pathology}} A contagious bacterial skin disease forming [[pustule]]s and yellow crusty sores, chiefly on the face and hands. It is common in children and infection is often through cuts or insect bites.

